Vendored data — WHATWG Encoding Standard index files
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The files under `vendor/whatwg/` are verbatim snapshots of the index tables and
label list from the WHATWG Encoding Standard:

    https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/

    index-*.txt              — encoder/decoder index tables
    index-iso-2022-jp-katakana.txt
    encodings.json           — the label → encoding map

Snapshot date: 2024-09-18 (per the `# Date:` / `# Identifier:` provenance headers
inside each file). These files are used to generate `Sources/Viceroy/Tables/*.swift`
via `Tools/viceroy-tablegen`; the generated Swift is checked in so building the
library needs no network and no generation step.

The WHATWG Encoding Standard and its index data are made available under the
terms described at https://spec.whatwg.org/ (CC BY 4.0 for the specification
text; the index tables are factual data / public domain). They are redistributed
here solely to make the build reproducible and are not modified.
